{
  "stem": "13079.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we put out a search for him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And finally it turned up that he was in-- being held at Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, I called Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Justice Jackson and told him if he could release Eigruber to me, I had a case there which would justify hanging him as high as Haman.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Justice Jackson said, well, that's pretty high.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So go right ahead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We'll let you have him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he took his seat along with 60 other accused in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was found guilty and was executed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His crimes were killing these prisoners [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who couldn't defend themselves at all, using these prisoners as guinea pigs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as such, not-- well, it-- it's-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think runs into not only morals that normal human beings are expected to have, but certainly was contrary to the medical profession to use persons that served as his guinea pigs and using them against that will.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These people didn't admit guilt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To them, there was never any guilt attached to their conduct.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Many of them, or rather none of them, ever expressed contrition in any form.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was ?] [? never ?] sorry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They thought that what they had done was correct.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that applied to everybody from the camp kommandant on down to the lowliest kapo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Eigruber was-- he-- his activity was expansive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had a concentration camp of his own in the sense that he had prisoners that he utilized in carrying out the functions of his office as well.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he, Eigruber, had participated in executions of prisoners that were sent to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
